    <a href="/en/archive/Stoltenbergs-2nd-Government/Ministry-of-Labour-and-Social-Inclusion/personer-og-enheter/politisk-ledelse/2006/state-secretary-raimo-valle.html?id=487117" title="">Former State Secretary Raimo Valle</a></p>        

